Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:40.08,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget, looking up at the sky from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:48.55,Song,,0,0,0,,The morning sun so beautiful, on spring days, just us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.52,0:22:56.72,Song,,0,0,0,,All the hardships and the sorrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.17,0:22:54.84,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.11,0:23:01.11,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:04.90,Song,,0,0,0,,Carry them away gently from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.57,0:23:11.81,Song,,0,0,0,,together with the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:22.25,Song,,0,0,0,,This vast, blue sky—may it never change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:31.83,Song,,0,0,0,,And may my dearest friends stay just the way they are.
